292
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:56,080
She is definitely crazy.

293
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,280
She's trying to ruin us.

294
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:01,960
Boss, then

295
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,840
